**Module 29: Python**
**Lab (68 minutes, Advanced)**

In this hands-on lab, advanced learners will dive into Python programming. You will:

* Implement complex data structures and algorithms
* Practice object-oriented programming concepts
* Work with external libraries and APIs
* Debug and optimize code

Through guided exercises and independent practice, you will reinforce your understanding of Python and develop practical skills. By the end of this lab, you will be able to design and implement efficient Python solutions to real-world problems.
